{"id": 674, "genre": 1001, "title": "有哪些都市传说听起来不会发生，但其实是真的？", "description": "真的，真的是真的。", "record_count": 8690, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194620raMyLZsxUWvAD4Eq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-05T01:02:36Z", "options": [{"id": 32001, "content": "大部分gay都结婚了，或者说，你认为结婚的都是异性恋，实际上，并不是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341765}, {"id": 32518, "content": "在大学不谈恋爱都觉得丢脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337846}, {"id": 32519, "content": "留名", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 40455, "content": "生活比小说还要狗血", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403174}, {"id": 31759, "content": "面包没有，爱情也会慢慢没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 252, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340352}, {"id": 32016, "content": "喝醉了之后会在马路上睡着，以前以为是段子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158443}, {"id": 32784, "content": "一千块能过一个月.一万块一个月不够花", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346512}, {"id": 32529, "content": "如今帅哥身边不一定配美女指不定就是美受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345275}, {"id": 31762, "content": "不要想的太美，做好最坏的打算，因为它绝对会发生⋯⋯∠( ᐛ 」∠)＿", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255022}, {"id": 31764, "content": "女人晚睡，胸部会变小。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340381}, {"id": 32021, "content": "只要错过一个不错的人，就会很久都找不到不错的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341885}, {"id": 31768, "content": "工资越来越少，工作越来越多，开销越来越大，前途越来越小……你的终点是别人的起跑线……最后还是回家抱娃吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248526}, {"id": 32281, "content": "到了40岁还想嫁人，天方夜谭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260759}, {"id": 31770, "content": "办公室恋情是雷区", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338553}, {"id": 31772, "content": "進來看到每一句話都像讀到一個故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236872}, {"id": 31774, "content": "工作后就熬不动夜了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200757dVn5p6mSbQT8cYtL.jpg", "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 31780, "content": "大学里一半的不是处", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301252}, {"id": 31781, "content": "打扮打扮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340427}, {"id": 31784, "content": "越清纯的女人，床上越骚。。。吃不消", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340417}, {"id": 31789, "content": "再丑也能找到男朋友。是真的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 187, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336872}, {"id": 32557, "content": "大学生的女神，毕业工作以后发现她是你老板啃嫩草的对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345332}, {"id": 32302, "content": "西直门真的走不出去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341784}, {"id": 33326, "content": "没有什么事是不可能的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349719}, {"id": 31797, "content": "一白遮百丑，一胖毁所有。胖人真的找不到男朋友……", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004642HRfMKJWkqr1tpu9F.jpg", "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205358}, {"id": 32053, "content": "世界上99%的人都是寄生虫（蠢货）", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200758Pv9DIVdyxSJuUYg5.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342174}, {"id": 31800, "content": "猪不能抬头看天", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340575}, {"id": 32568, "content": "好多程序猿，射击湿在哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338864}, {"id": 32313, "content": "越是吃货，越是说要减肥了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343196}, {"id": 32058, "content": "说好的暑假不补课，学校还是迎风而上，不顾后果", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342206}, {"id": 31803, "content": "我有好多好多想去完成的事情，但是就是没有时间，可怜了我们这种万年加班族……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334734}, {"id": 31805, "content": "男人对女人一见钟情无非是因为荷尔蒙", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340506}, {"id": 32061, "content": "我就一进来看一个叫刘小鑫是文艺青年在刷屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340997}, {"id": 31812, "content": "没有一顿烤串儿解决不了的恩怨，如果有，就两顿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134059}, {"id": 31814, "content": "单身狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223684}, {"id": 32070, "content": "本命年真的有诅咒", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340608}, {"id": 31816, "content": "买买买吃吃吃治百病", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114642}, {"id": 34376, "content": "不知道‘都市传说’是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360552}, {"id": 31819, "content": "Fuck ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340720}, {"id": 31821, "content": "我有女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254650}, {"id": 31825, "content": "風塵女子都有個弟弟要上學", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340815}, {"id": 31826, "content": "只要意志坚强，就可以单身狗就可以戒撸？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235023}, {"id": 35154, "content": "大学不知道是干嘛的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315426}, {"id": 32084, "content": "别不信，到头来我们都得加入到建设中国特色社会主义的队伍中去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342437}, {"id": 31830, "content": "什么是都市传说？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334517}, {"id"